<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246075>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Hyphessobrycon lucenorum, paratypes: a) MZUSP 115522, female, 32, 9 mm SL; b) UFRO-I 22724, male, 29, 1 mm SL, immediately after capture." ;
